reviewText: Bought this for the pilot episode of Mr. Ed but loved Lassie episodes too.

At least when I bought it.

Got it for the never aired Mr Ed pilot.... interesting differences. Script much the same with aired pilot, but completely different cast (but Ed of course, of course ;) and sets.

The Lassie stuff a nice bonus.

Quality was good, considering all probably from not top quality, circulated 16mm film prints.
